2ba6ff\" data-hs-link-id=\"0\" data-hs-link-id-v2=\"FvEt5vUg\" target=\"_blank\">Join us tomorrow</a> (Wednesday) as two visual pros show how to turn a basic build into something that feels premium, all inside Bolt.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:175%\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:175%\">Laurel Beyers (designer + UX consultant) and Clark Wimberly (design engineer + agency owner) will answer your questions and explain a ton of practical ways to sharpen your site’s design:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"line-height:175%\">\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Smart planning and UX strategy that actually saves time</li>\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\">How to use prompts to nail your aesthetic faster</li>\r\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Adding fonts, icons, and polish that make clients go “woah”</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:175%\">You’ll definitely walk away with something you hadn’t thought of before…personally, we can’t wait. <a href=\"https://d5llC804.na1.hubspotlinks.com/Ctc/DQ+113/d5llC804/VVD58x82SQy9VTCk1Q2PnJVtW1c61D75DF8ngN2SX22Y5gg4xW50kH_H6lZ3kyW3dmZcy93W-7sW4p1kvN68SjfTW1LJv8m6bSgjRW8YC2cf7d4kr8W6sWnQW3pRKHdW7qQkQ99kmqnNN8CnqCtW50prW95dk3v1YPRW0N66GrLnlPK1VW6G9Fy17rmHgkW1XXY8c3kNT0sN58t6tC67r3fW8wtGn84Gg5p9N2Y-335ZBqrmW2bCbpF2W-MbZW7d5T152BknNlW7B3psS3nHNkCW5wzFVh6GkSPnVR-g6-7bw9gpN8RMW-7x2RfDW5N_7yZ67-tGjW9gyd8S8p6sTgV-449r4WC7sQW8dhDZM3ZRtkbVLHS953NW6swW7vBQXb70nHwXW15F2ZN2_R0gJVm-NpW37VfHRW85Zd1k5VvBnVW4PSfHN12nv0zW7c4yTK6q2w-JW3jJ_Zj2HskV_f50Fs2H04\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color:#2ba6ff\" data-hs-link-id=\"0\" data-hs-link-id-v2=\"d2cALsrD\" target=\"_blank\">RSVP now&nbsp;→</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:175%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin:0; line-height:175%; font-size:22px\">Connect your existing Supabase database&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:175%\">You can now bring your own Supabase database to your projects.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:175%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:175%\">Head to&nbsp;<strong data-stringify-type=\"bold\">Settings → Database → Advanced</strong>&nbsp;and look for the new \"Connect to an existing database\" option. Point it at your Supabase project and you\'re good to go.If you already have a database configured, we\'ll show you a heads up before making any changes.</p></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_module_17604521579172\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"color: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\"><table class=\"hse-image-wrapper\" role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n  <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td class=\"hs_padded\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif; color:#000000; word-break:break-word; text-align:center; padding:10px 20px; font-size:0px\">\r\n        <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://hs-45403856.f.hubspotemail.net/hub/45403856/hubfs/supabase-connect-ex.jpg?width=1120&amp;upscale=true&amp;name=supabase-connect-ex.jpg\" style=\"outline:none; text-decoration:none; max-width:100%; font-size:16px\" width=\"560\" align=\"middle\">\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n</table></div>\r\n  <table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"\" style=\"\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"hs_padded\" style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif; font-size:15px; color:#000000; word-break:break-word; padding:10px 20px\"><div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_module_17604519856821\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"color: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\"><div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_module_17604519856821_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text\" style=\"color: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widge