(191, 'description', NULL, 'Fresh design strats, new fonts, smarter prompts, and then some. Also ICYMI, here&rsquo;s &ldquo;What&rsquo;s new in Bolt v2&rdquo;!\r\n\r\nHey builders,\r\n\r\nThis week we&rsquo;re focusing on how to take your site from simple to stunning (and making sure you&rsquo;re making the most of Bolt v2).\r\n\r\nIs your site looking too &ldquo;starter project&rdquo;?\r\n\r\nJoin us tomorrow (https://d5llC804.na1.hubspotlinks.com/Ctc/DQ+113/d5llC804/VVD58x82SQy9VTCk1Q2PnJVtW1c61D75DF8ngN2SX2503gVDYW95jsWP6lZ3ppN14v7vTs8n6lW5YwT5k55QQ_rW8fjS3n5gttW0MH6Hffj7KxPN4KgW95hHmhJW8hrgRt1TL-lMW2nN7Dr1kynf5W1ZWCN76S-L5cW97_Npc98rGbZW41DRmp2NdX_9W65-XHS5GSJPtW1Pg8Z97lzKXQW2wJbfp3XwCr1W2-wpz35XXLMcW6JZpDs7t0y1zW3NLhlP2dx0BpW393ZLl3l11bzW94lRKB7hWndpW7Md69L6LFLnGW1HZv-T8zTg6fW4C75Vy8ngNCmW46sHJM79K1RLN2SKSjknZM9PW6pqyZ16XL77FW17ZMD690JrGYW47Kkx85T0MXzV9PPkG2nR9swW1-5J_N4vGmf7W7WWMXx4pZmb3W4-zKQK1nPghNf6rKvMM04 ) (Wednesday) as two visual pros show how to turn a basic build into something that feels premium, all inside Bolt.\r\n\r\nLaurel Beyers (designer + UX consultant) and Clark Wimberly (design engineer + agency owner) will answer your questions and explain a ton of practical ways to sharpen your site&rsquo;s design:\r\n\r\n- Smart planning and UX strategy that actually saves time\r\n- How to use prompts to nail your aesthetic faster\r\n- Adding fonts, icons, and polish that make clients go &ldquo;woah&rdquo;\r\n\r\nYou&rsquo;ll definitely walk away with something you hadn&rsquo;t thought of before&hellip;personally, we can&rsquo;t wait. RSVP now &rarr; (https://d5llC804.na1.hubspotlinks.com/Ctc/DQ+113/d5llC804/VVD58x82SQy9VTCk1Q2PnJVtW1c61D75DF8ngN2SX22Y5fr76W50kH_H6lZ3nXW5rfm-t3WFKQdW1BDH3R468PN4W3bRprv3LBjkYW6y-Ndf1SQyn1W37Pn894KkM5mW1M7rP33Rr-WjMxS08ljq807W5_YKlc1K1ZBCW1Xy72J7mzRzTW902j3d6YYpM0VQkMKs3dQVWHW3sPwkQ7WQpC5W4lYYH13pd0tdW4bKLm85J4P5WV2Prnx7JStqhW89kvgX4Hn8SYW6xGM-T1D5c_tW9gTqt38ry76TW8Krhh92cZStFW3sjt9T7QlvXbW8ch7ht1mDZlnW8cxGq058MNKGW7d_rbq6rr6qZVLMhqX7KHVVXW4kFKtk3vq6gdW7bPj6t5SDFtdW34gb0Q1fY71GMxzKBr5L-p6W2h4YSL8Wv66mN5RKwxD7PkWpW4t5Nmv6Lht24W2MbdTM78jgDYdNw8fb04 )\r\n\r\nConnect your existing Supabase database\r\n\r\nYou can now bring your own Supabase database to your projects.\r\n\r\nHead to Settings &rarr; Database &rarr; Advanced and look for the new &quot;Connect to an existing database&quot; option. Point it at your Supabase project and you&#039;re good to go.If you already have a database configured, we&#039;ll show you a heads up before making any changes.\r\n\r\nICYMI: What&rsquo;s New in Bolt v2\r\n\r\nMissed last week&rsquo;s livestream? We covered everything new in Bolt v2: planning mode, database updates, integrations, and more. Catch the replay when you have a moment. Check out What&#039;s new in Bolt v2 &rarr; (https://d5llC804.na1.hubspotlinks.com/Ctc/DQ+113/d5llC804/VVD58x82SQy9VTCk1Q2PnJVtW1c61D75DF8ngN2SX23R3gVDYW6N1vHY6lZ3pkW4tZb271LTlbQW64pPSD24dTk5VKPlCr7CgvyRW2pZ4hk3QNF7zW2DKmBD2mVJ3jW6c55L_1rr6flW1JC1MW7TlQmwW4QWlB-1j4Jf1W4gbHbs1-cXLpW5j3rw17XWdyMW2pdS842pf_fqW5c-Zlh3ywh0KN93Ds235LlmkW11RtYf3wpSgwW2ZYDfB6SBHcVVzdF_W5-nlTSW3xr01V8lz-5rW8SlGQq541XcdW4MrG787Z3hKfVw42xS7n0_bgW39phWQ783bWjV6vGYd95b9czf1bhtCn04 )\r\n\r\nHappy building,\r\n\r\nEric Simons\r\n\r\nCEO &amp; Co-Founder, Bolt.new (https://d5llC804.na1.hubspotlinks.com/Ctc/DQ+113/d5llC804/VVD58x82SQy9VTCk1Q2PnJVtW1c61D75DF8ngN2SX23x3lcq-W69sMD-6lZ3lpW6nmwS95P4MpvW86hrjP11QvCTW78wkrK19tR09W8TbPgK9h5RkhV6p6VF5qk3n5N7GZcNdK9DTdW4GMzyc8qTkXsW38h3ZK6bdVF6N33dC4rZ2gKyVqJJLF8Lpp3MV2R_8_2GMW7VW1Kkspf4C7zysW3hstn169fsqkW60ch_531bzKcW1qVYHm1KQcvlW1xsmn55_dSSpW8y_29Z5M5pnJW2C9ptd5n_0TGW8F9cGH3rfrtPW87lMz941-yrkf6c0cZ204 )\r\n\r\nStackBlitz, Inc., 2443 Fillmore Street #380-16814, San Francisco, CA, 94115, United States. To opt out of future emails from StackBlitz, click here to unsubscribe (https://hs-45403856.s.hubspotemail.net/hs/preferences-center/en/page?data=W2nXS-N30h-GhW45DRyj1_b8GnW1L72xS22W0wZW3j4RYP41S8t7W2-DK6432zp9gW3BM1D